| IPFS issues (content availability) | Low | Medium | Pin via Pinata + multiple gateways. |
| Gas/fee spikes (even on Arc) | Low | Low | Monitoring + a minimum reward floor ($1–2). |
| Security (a bug in BountyAdapter) | Low | High | Full test suite + fork tests + a planned audit. |

All critical dependencies are on official Arc infrastructure only (audited by the Arc team).

